Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.29,Signs,,0,0,0,,Dati otkaz
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala vam na svemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:11.50,Signs,,0,0,0,,Otarasi se stvari
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sve ukupno će biti oko 30.000.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:16.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,Banka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:17.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,Išida Šoja
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sve podižem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:26.14,Signs,,0,0,0,,Vraćam ti novac
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:58.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,Poslednji dan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:32.29,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs100}Oblik glasa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.15,Signs,,0,0,0,,Odeljenje 6-2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedite na svoja mesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Od danas imate novu drugaricu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta 'oćeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Imaš sreće, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Devojčica je.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš me briga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirni?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro, možeš da se predstaviš.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:56.73,Signs,,0,0,0,,Za razgovore
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je. Ja sam Nišimija Šoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:12.33,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nadam se da ću moći da se sprijateljim sa vama uz pomoć ove sveske.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:16.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,Slobodno je koristite kada želite da pričate sa mnom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:31.51,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ja sam gluva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Zezaš!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.15,Signs,,0,0,0,,Pozdrav, Nišimija. Ja sam Kavai Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Eto, drago mi je.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, umeš li ti da pričaš japanski?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao, kakva si.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,Možeš li da ponoviš?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Imaš li neki nadimak?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Odustajem! Predajem se!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo, je li?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Isti kao Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaže da joj je nadimak Šo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš fino.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Baš nije.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro, zapišite sledeće odeljke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Od strane 20 do strane 25, i vežbajte probleme sa strane 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To će biti na sledećem kontrolnom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Daj mi tvoju svesku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Prva je tačka oslonca. Kako joj ime kaže, oslonac je za polugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Zatim je tu sila primenjena na jednu stranu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I na kraju teret koji se podiže ili spušta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Zavisno od lokacije, postoje tri vrste poluga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, poranila si.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ću ti reći kada da počneš, u redu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo ponovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ćemo ovako ići na takmičenje?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemamo šanse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo ti je kazna za to što si jadan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Auć, boli.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Boli!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Znate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Opet nisam mogla da se skoncentrišem pola časa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kopiraću ti moje beleške posle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ja nisam ništa zgrešio.\NZato se nikada neću izviniti—"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Na šta to liči, Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboravi. Dalje.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cvikeraš jedan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Počinješ odavde.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Pvekini viže da budež tvdogvav,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,vekva je majka, uždahnuži.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Neču da še ižvinim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sledeći, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mora da me zezaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne zavitlavaj se, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:50.21,Signs,,0,0,0,,Možete li da mi kažete o čemu ste pričale?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo nazad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ćao, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Znaš šta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako ne budeš pažljivija, zamrzeće te svi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pvijatelji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Odvratna si!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam Kita iz udruženja gluvih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li ste čuli za znakovni jezik?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To je jezik gde pričate rukama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Možete da vodite čitave razgovore koristeći samo ruke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije divno?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.36,Alt,,0,0,0,,Znakovni jezik...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I šta kažete na ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Da biste mogli više da pričate sa Šoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,da li biste hteli da posvetite tri minuta dnevno učenju znakovnog jezika?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nastavnice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije dovoljno da pišemo u njenu svesku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bilo bi lakše za Šoko ako bi mogla da koristi znakovni jezik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali meni je lakše da pišem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ću naučiti znakovni jezik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.19,Signs,,0,0,0,,Pokaži mi "Sahara Mijoko" znakovnim jezikom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hada...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,jo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sa."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulizice jedna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Obožavam ga. Tako je kul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A, biće u seriji sledeće nedelje. Ne smem to da propustim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar joj odeća nije baš jadna?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj naglas, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovom knjigom je autor hteo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Čak i nakon eksperimenta, mangan dioksid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hirose, ti uzmi tu stranu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nišimija..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš, Išida?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I zvezdica.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, preteruješ, bre.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Misliš? Ja mislim da je ovo taman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji si zloća.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Koga briga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro izgleda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:21.76,Signs,,0,0,0,,Svaka čast, Nišimija! Sahara je otišla negde.\NNauči nas da govorimo nišimijanskim! Jej! Jej!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,U, joj, ko li je ovo uradio?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako zlobno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ću obrisati ovo za tebe, u redu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sve čisto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:59.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nema na čemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokom perioda Đomon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, bre, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Usred časa smo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, izvinjavam se!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde smo sad stali...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, u kakvim su kućama živeli.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Iznenadila si se, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li zapravo možeš da čuješ kada nosiš ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno, to sam se i ja pitala.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pokaži mi ih na trenutak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Daj da vidim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, šta je ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Odvratno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(60,38.925)}Jesi li rekla nešto?\NGlupačo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1860,38.925)}Kakve mišiće imam!\NMišić-mija Šoko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija, jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta da radimo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Preterao si, bre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Zbornica
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Taj cvikeraš me baš nervira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je? Pomeri se.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Smetaš nam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ona to radi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.49,Signs,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta lupetaš? Ako imaš neki problem, reci tako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pusti me! Odvratna si!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, Nišimija je zanimljiva.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Šoja je skroz pocrveneo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Idemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ona to radi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Skroz je opičena.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se, Šoja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sutra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Postoji nešto o čemu moramo da popričamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,U pitanju je Nišimija Šoko, koja je odsutna danas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Njena majka nas je kontaktirala juče.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Osam njenih slušnih aparata su nestali ili pokvareni u proteklih pet meseci.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Njena majka veruje da je maltretiraju u školi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li je iko od vas primetio da neko maltretira ili se loše ponaša prema Nišimiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Čini se da su slušni aparati jako skupi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim vas da ne pravite više problema svojim roditeljima...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To si bio ti, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:16:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ustani više!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ti si sedela pored njega, šta kažeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguće da je zadirkivao pomalo, sa vremena na vreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A ti, Šimada?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, ja sam mu rekao da prestane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali on me nije slušao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Šimada, i ti si kriv koliko i ja!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A i devojčice su je stalno ogovarale iza leđa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pogotovo Ueno i Kavai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja to nikada ne bih uradila!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si takav?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, užasan si!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rasplakao ju je...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.44,Signs,,0,0,0,,Za razgovore\NNišimija Šoko, odeljenje 6-2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Otkud ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:17.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(60,38.925)}O čemu ste pričale?\NSkapiraj sama.\NIzvinite.\NOtišle smo jer si spora!\NGlupačo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:17.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1860,38.925)}Šta nam treba za sutra?\NKompas.\NHvala ti.\NŠta je učitelj rekao?\NNe znam, ne čujem. <3\NIzvini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, razumem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinjavam se zbog svega.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, naravno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Doviđenja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Šoja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stani, Šoja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoj učitelj mi je sve ispričao.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj, zašto si tako mokar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosadna si. Skočio sam sa mosta kao i uvek.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stani!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li pravio probleme drugima?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da me smaraš.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li istina to što je tvoj učitelj rekao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, istina je!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Idemo kod Nišimije.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Spremi se.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.46,Signs,,0,0,0,,Banka Mizuho
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo kući, Šo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Od sutra budi dobar dečak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,U redu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Zvali su ih "došljacima", i imali su mnoge probleme.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, šta to radiš sa mojim stolom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta si to radila, gadiš mi se!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Opet taj izraz lica.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekini da izigravaš dobricu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je? Ako želiš nešto da kažeš, reci to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne razumem taj tvoj glupav izraz lica,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,i nerviraš me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde, reci više!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si to uradila?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je sa tobom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudim še...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudim še naibole što mogu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to govoriš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:21:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je, bre?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:21:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne razumem!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:25.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,Gubi se, Išida.\NKada ćeš više da nestaneš?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno me nervira...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija je promenila školu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To je to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, ko je bio redar juče?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam dobio spisak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I ko je bio zadužen za cveće?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:12.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,Časovi znakovnog jezika
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Šoko, zdravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sećaš li me se?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.17,0:23:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Iz šestog razreda.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.88,0:23:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida Šoja.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.88,0:24:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.08,0:24:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.29,0:24:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.55,0:24:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.44,0:24:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.53,0:24:32.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,Za razgovore\NNišimija Šoko, odeljenje 6-2
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.52,0:24:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Došao sam ovo da ti vratim.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.87,0:24:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Izgubila si je.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.60,0:24:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto znam znakovni jezik?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.82,0:24:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Naučio sam ga.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.06,0:24:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,U svakom slučaju, evo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.63,0:24:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mada možda ne želiš da je vidiš.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.06,0:25:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.88,0:25:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja i ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.59,0:25:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li bismo mogli da budemo prijatelji?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.37,0:25:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to ja govorim?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.45,0:25:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj, pa ona je isto govorila onda u osnovnoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.90,0:25:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Konačno sam shvatio.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.08,0:25:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da plačeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.61,0:25:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da plačeš, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.15,0:25:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li bismo mogli da budemo prijatelji?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.93,0:25:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.71,0:25:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.91,0:25:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.39,0:25:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Probudi se!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.84,0:25:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Vreme je za doručak!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.49,0:26:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Probudi se, Šo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.16,0:26:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro jutro, Marija.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.07,0:26:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo je ustao!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.68,0:26:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Odoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.44,0:26:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ćao, mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.86,0:26:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Srećno danas.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.87,0:26:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Evo, Šo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.28,0:26:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatno.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.30,0:26:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Jedi koliko voliš.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.09,0:26:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto se tako smeškaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.65,0:26:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, znaš...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.04,0:26:54.25,Signs,,0,0,0,,Vraćam ti novac
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.68,0:26:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Puno si radio za ovo, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.25,0:27:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Čak si prodao i svoje mange, odeću i dušek.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.96,0:27:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali srećna sam što si bio spreman toliko da učiniš.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.84,0:27:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nego, Šo...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.61,0:27:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si poželeo da se ubiješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.12,0:27:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pa, svašta se izdešavalo...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.49,0:27:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali znaš, više...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.44,0:27:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako sam i mislila.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.54,0:27:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Znači bila sam u pravu!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.91,0:27:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Znala sam da nešto ne valja!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.15,0:27:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoja soba je bila previše čista!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.93,0:27:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam mogla da te dobijem na telefon!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.04,0:27:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I kakav je ono zlokoban kalendar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.46,0:27:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sve stranice nakon aprila su bile istrgnute...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.06,0:27:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako mi ne obećaš da ćeš odustati od toga, spaliću sve.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.39,0:27:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Spaliću 1,7 miliona jena koje si svojim znojem zaradio!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.27,0:27:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej! Slušaš li me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.81,0:27:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.94,0:27:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.24,0:27:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta {\i1}ti{\i0} radiš, nesrećni sine moj!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.36,0:28:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček... Izvini!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.05,0:28:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Istinski se izvinjavam!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.45,0:28:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Neću to uraditi!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.43,0:28:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Neću to uraditi! Izvini! Stvarno!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.14,0:28:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta nećeš uraditi! Lepo mi reci!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.83,0:28:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Neću se ubiti!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.77,0:28:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Neću pokušati da se ubijem!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.53,0:28:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.41,0:28:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.36,0:28:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.63,0:28:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Obećao si, u redu?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.99,0:28:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.07,0:28:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Auć!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.19,0:28:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,V-Vodu!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.45,0:28:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Juče sam planirao da skočim sa visokog mosta i umrem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.06,0:28:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To što sam otišao da vidim Nišimiju je bila samo priprema.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.58,0:28:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bio je to najveći test hrabrosti mog života.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.39,0:28:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ali...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.50,0:29:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatelji...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.19,0:29:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta sam to učinio?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.23,0:29:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tokom ceremonije upisa u nižu srednju, čuo sam Šimadu...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.95,0:29:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bolje se ne približavaj liku po imenu Išida Šoja.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.58,0:29:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,On je maltretirao ljude.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.92,0:29:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shvatio sam da se gresi koje počiniš uvek vraćaju da te progone
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.36,0:29:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}i da ću morati uvek da ih nosim sa sobom i prihvatim sve kazne koje me snađu.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.07,0:29:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tako...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.68,0:29:48.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kreten
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.86,0:29:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ostao sam sasvim sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.39,0:30:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro onda.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.70,0:30:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Prevedite ovo za sledeći čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.40,0:30:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.45,0:30:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.48,0:30:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kavai.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.35,0:30:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li predao svoj domaći iz matematike?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.19,0:30:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A, izvini. Zaboravio sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.18,0:30:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.45,0:30:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, onda bolje požuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.33,0:30:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoću, izvini.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.55,0:30:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.73,0:31:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo u dvorište?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.37,0:31:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Išida je tako uvek sam, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.42,0:31:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Poznat je po tome. Svi znaju za to."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.40,0:31:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozbiljno?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.86,0:31:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"A, opet gleda ovamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.93,0:31:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zar nije usamljen tako, uvek sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.82,0:31:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoće li tako provesti ceo život?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.97,0:31:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zašto li uopšte živi?"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.80,0:31:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.12,0:31:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kupio sam ovo na dan izlaska.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.93,0:31:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Mislim da ću da prestanem da budem fan onda.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.24,0:31:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.29,0:31:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa da.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.17,0:31:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.26,0:31:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozbiljno?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.13,0:32:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ta frizura mi deluje poznato.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.16,0:32:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ko to beše?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.28,0:32:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nego...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.81,0:32:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Smem li uopšte opet da vidim Nišimiju?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.09,0:32:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rekla je da često hrani šarane hlebom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.59,0:32:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ali kako ja da joj izađem pred lice?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.19,0:32:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Možda da se izvinim što sam je rasplakao?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.81,0:32:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rekla je da je tamo utorkom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.40,0:32:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Da li bih joj smetao?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.03,0:32:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Vratih se.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.53,0:33:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.17,0:33:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Iznenadi me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.34,0:33:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.64,0:33:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini za ono jutros.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.22,0:33:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Što sam spalila novac za koji si tako vredno radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.10,0:33:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali znaš, ne bih ni želela da koristim novac koji si zaradio sa ciljem da umreš.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.77,0:33:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.76,0:33:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaradiću ga ponovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.13,0:33:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A, hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.21,0:33:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da žuriš.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.40,0:33:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde, sigurno si gladan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.03,0:33:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde da jedemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.97,0:33:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gladna!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.58,0:33:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Utorak...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.84,0:34:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, možeš li da mi pozajmiš svoj bicikl?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.02,0:34:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ja?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.09,0:34:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha? Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.08,0:34:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A, to je onaj lik.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.10,0:34:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nešto sam zaboravio.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.92,0:34:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Idem da ga pokupim.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.31,0:34:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Zašto sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.35,0:34:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Koristi svoj bicikl.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.28,0:34:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pitam te zato što nemam svoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.18,0:34:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekini.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.14,0:34:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pusti, bre.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.29,0:34:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, prekini.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.97,0:34:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Neka mi neko pomogne!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.39,0:34:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ej...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.52,0:34:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pomozite mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.06,0:34:27.50,Alt,,0,0,0,,Do vraga!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.77,0:34:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.72,0:34:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pomozite mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.04,0:34:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiri se, bre!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.04,0:34:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pusti to!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.07,0:34:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.73,0:34:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Možeš da uzmeš moj.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.70,0:34:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.74,0:34:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji si car.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.04,0:34:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nije mi ga vratio.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.22,0:34:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I baš danas na utorak.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.99,0:34:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Možda je to neki znak - da ne idem?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.28,0:35:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nije da ne mogu i peške da odem,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.93,0:35:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ali kao da mi nešto govori "Ne idi!".
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.81,0:35:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nedostaje mi neki izgovor...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.66,0:35:07.29,Signs,,0,0,0,,Pufnasti novi hleb\NKupon za popust
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.88,0:35:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Treba mi neki fini, skroz prirodni razlog da odem.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.41,0:35:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kupon za popust na pufnasti hleb?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.46,0:35:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To je to!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.12,0:35:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Da li je Nišimija možda tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.56,0:35:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.60,0:35:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, tamo je.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.69,0:35:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.11,0:35:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija Šoko nije ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.44,0:35:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, ali,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.04,0:35:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,jesi li ti stvarno njen prijatelj?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.92,0:35:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Doviđenja.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.84,0:35:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije ništa.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.68,0:35:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Istrčao je neki miš.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.15,0:35:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Neki skroz ljigavi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.04,0:36:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne brini. Neće se vraćati.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.23,0:36:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatelji...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.58,0:36:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.64,0:36:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.15,0:36:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A, tu si!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.92,0:36:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.81,0:36:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidi ovo!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.00,0:36:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo je tvoj bicikl, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.28,0:36:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobar tajming!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.77,0:36:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je što je pisala tvoja adresa na njemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.55,0:36:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde si ga našao?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.80,0:36:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bio je odbačen u polju pirinča.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.06,0:36:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Čoveče, baš sam ga tražio.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.70,0:36:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je što sam uspeo da ti ga vratim.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.15,0:37:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo, Išida?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.05,0:37:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A, ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.03,0:37:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako se beše zoveš?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.55,0:37:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka, bre.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.45,0:37:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedim iza tebe, znaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.06,0:37:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A, tako je. Ovo je dobar hleb.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.09,0:37:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš malo, Nagacuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.28,0:37:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.79,0:37:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.42,0:37:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro jutro.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.04,0:37:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro jutro.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.45,0:37:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.28,0:37:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo negde posle škole.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.47,0:37:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pošto smo sad prijatelji.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.27,0:37:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovamo, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.64,0:38:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo, Jašo?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.23,0:38:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Ništa.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.55,0:38:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, "Jašo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.99,0:38:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kao da smo "veliki" prijatelji, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.96,0:38:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I? Nešto te muči?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.36,0:38:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Slobodno možeš da mi ispričaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.03,0:38:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi smo najbolji prijatelji.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.04,0:38:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci, Nagacuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.84,0:38:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta su uopšte prijatelji?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.31,0:38:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tipa, postoji li nešto što moraš da ispuniš da bi imao prava da budeš nekome prijatelj?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.42,0:38:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gle, Jašo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.51,0:38:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ispruži ruku.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.44,0:39:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To su prijatelji.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.74,0:39:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidiš, Išida,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.09,0:39:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,ja mislim da prijateljstvo prkosi logici i rečima.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.53,0:39:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakva prava, kakvi bakrači?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.98,0:39:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Glupost.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.96,0:39:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.68,0:39:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ali tu je.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.77,0:39:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.21,0:39:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, ti si—
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.72,0:39:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam njen dečko.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.64,0:39:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A, joj, pade.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.02,0:39:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislim hleb, ne ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.18,0:39:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali, ko bi rekao...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.56,0:39:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija voli mlađe momke?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.69,0:39:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, to je nekako neočekivano.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.52,0:39:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A, ovaj, uzmi bar ovaj hleb.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.76,0:39:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobar je.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.56,0:39:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.66,0:39:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako si došao ovde samo da bi se bolje osećao, odlazi.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.56,0:39:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li to sve?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.92,0:40:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doviđenja.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.92,0:40:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, momak!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.41,0:40:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Moj ortak ti kaže da želi da vidi Nišimiju!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.56,0:40:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.38,0:40:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne smaraj i zovi je ovamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.77,0:40:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Otkud ti ovde, Nagacuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.95,0:40:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pratio sam te.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.96,0:40:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Najbolji smo prijatelji, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.63,0:40:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I za bednike važi - sličan se sa sličnim druži.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.43,0:40:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Seronja.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.97,0:40:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim? Šta je tvoj problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.11,0:40:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Usudi se da to kažeš opet!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.86,0:40:27.52,Alt,,0,0,0,,Čekaj, Nagacuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.25,0:40:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Seronja!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.20,0:40:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidi ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.29,0:40:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta se dešava?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.84,0:40:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije to Juzuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.14,0:40:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pobogu.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.95,0:40:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Svađaju se.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.36,0:40:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.02,0:40:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.67,0:40:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde da stanemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.67,0:40:40.16,Alt,,0,0,0,,Povuci to!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.16,0:40:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde, Nagacuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.43,0:40:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosta više. Idemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.88,0:40:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.04,0:40:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bre, ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.38,0:40:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A, zar ti nisi onaj od pre neki dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.53,0:40:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne, pomešali ste me...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.49,0:40:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, Nagacuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.63,0:40:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Auć!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.50,0:40:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do vraga!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.35,0:41:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Prokletstvo, sreli su se.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.16,0:41:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Svaka čast, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.16,0:41:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, momak.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.34,0:41:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nameravaš da ih špijuniraš?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.61,0:41:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Daj i meni da vidim!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.47,0:41:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.59,0:41:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida nekako čudno maše rukama.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.59,0:41:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To je znakovni jezik.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.08,0:41:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.60,0:41:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Strava.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.16,0:41:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam znao da to ume.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.39,0:41:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, i ti znaš znakovni jezik?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.10,0:41:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Prevedi mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.86,0:41:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ko je onaj seronja od malopre?"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.98,0:41:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Neki skroz mi nepoznati lik."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.78,0:41:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Baš je odvratan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.64,0:41:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Prevedi lepo!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.91,0:41:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pusti me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.97,0:41:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da padneš, momak.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.68,0:41:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Da budem iskren, mislio sam da je bolje da ne dolazim pred tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.68,0:41:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Proveo sam prethodne dve nedelje razmišljajući o smislu prijateljstva.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.26,0:42:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tražio sam razlog da se ponovo vidimo."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.06,0:42:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.57,0:42:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Drago mi je.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.26,0:42:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I ja sam razmišljala o tome.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.69,0:42:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Smešno je, zar ne?"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.78,0:42:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.41,0:42:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvoli, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.71,0:42:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hleb. Za šarane.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.16,0:42:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Voliš da ih hraniš?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.07,0:42:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A, da.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.08,0:42:51.13,Signs,,0,0,0,,Za razgovore\NNišimija Šoko, odeljenje 6-2
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.51,0:43:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija, verovatno je bolje da ipak ne gledaš unutra.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.49,0:43:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj, Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.83,0:43:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uskočila je...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.55,0:43:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.49,0:43:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li se nešto desilo Išidi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.82,0:43:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, momak!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.57,0:43:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida je skočio u reku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.84,0:43:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.84,0:43:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Auć!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.90,0:43:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta radiš, bre?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.70,0:43:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, šta je ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.60,0:43:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.83,0:44:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.50,0:44:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, ispala mi je.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.78,0:44:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš, Šoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.82,0:44:45.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sme li iko da mi izađe na crtu?\NIšida Šoja
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.27,0:44:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eto ti, na.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.79,0:44:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li videla ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.87,0:44:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta, bre? Zar to nije Išida?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.56,0:44:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Vidimo se ponovo"...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.42,0:45:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno joj ne smeta?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.05,0:45:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.94,0:45:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo si ti, Išida, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.19,0:45:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.58,0:45:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Š-Šta je ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.20,0:45:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, pođi sa mnom do zbornice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.53,0:45:23.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,Suspenzija od nedelju dana - Išida Šoja
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.58,0:45:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Skočio sam sa mosta Suimon u reku uprkos tome što je to zabranjeno,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.12,0:45:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,i zatim sam tu sliku okačio na internet..."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.36,0:45:33.16,Alt,,0,0,0,,Šoja!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.28,0:45:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, ali možeš li da odeš da pokupiš Mariju?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.51,0:45:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne smem da izlazim dok sam suspendovan.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.22,0:45:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma hajde, malo, šta fali?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.36,0:45:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala unapred.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.45,0:45:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček—
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.76,0:45:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej, bre...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.36,0:46:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Vreme je da idemo kući, Marija.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.87,0:46:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.58,0:46:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Neko je unutra!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.79,0:46:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.34,0:46:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.40,0:46:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.00,0:46:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nisi ti Nišimijin dečko?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.41,0:46:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Prehladićeš se.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.38,0:46:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A, pa to je onaj miš.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.20,0:46:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta radiš na ovakvom mestu?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.52,0:46:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde ti je obuća?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.13,0:46:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne ljutiš se?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.11,0:46:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Zbog čega?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.95,0:46:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam okačio onu tvoju sliku na internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.52,0:46:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A, to si bio ti?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.59,0:46:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Čoveče, koliko mi je laknulo što si to bio ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.37,0:47:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta pričaš to?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.87,0:47:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislim, nekako mi je jasno zašto si to uradio.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.43,0:47:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Naljuti se na mene onda.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.85,0:47:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne, ne mogu.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.71,0:47:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To sam zaslužio.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.98,0:47:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.21,0:47:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gladna sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.69,0:47:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dolazim.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.16,0:47:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Odoh onda ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.16,0:47:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I ti piči kući što pre.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.61,0:47:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoje dete?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.98,0:47:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Auć!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.55,0:47:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sestrino!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.77,0:47:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.19,0:47:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Evo, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.41,0:47:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jedi koliko voliš.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.68,0:47:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde je sestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.23,0:47:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rekla je da će kasniti večeras.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.53,0:47:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Je l' ti nije vruće, Marija?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.31,0:47:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ukusno je!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.66,0:47:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Super.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.33,0:47:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Juzuru, ne jedeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.56,0:47:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.59,0:48:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci "a"!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.80,0:48:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.39,0:48:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do vraga...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.04,0:48:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.34,0:48:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Iznenadih se kad si nestao.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.92,0:49:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Evo, kišobran.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.55,0:49:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma samo ga uzmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.83,0:49:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozbiljan sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.73,0:49:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eto.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.47,0:49:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A, nego...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.25,0:49:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako sam i mislio.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.72,0:49:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš ove?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.24,0:49:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Moje su, ali ih više ne nosim.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.22,0:49:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Daću ti ih.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.84,0:49:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si pobegao od kuće?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.62,0:49:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Posvađao sam se sa Šoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.15,0:49:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.22,0:49:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Znači ono, kao, problemi u vašoj vezi, i tako to?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.44,0:49:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Koristio sam njen šampon a da je nisam pitao.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.58,0:49:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oterala me je iz kuće.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.96,0:49:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, vi živite zajedno?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.52,0:49:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Drži kišobran nad sobom.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.83,0:49:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Imamo samo jedan, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.29,0:50:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, ja sam kriv što nisam poneo dva.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.89,0:50:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A i ako se prehladiš, kako ću da izađem Nišimiji pred oči?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.19,0:50:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušaj...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.05,0:50:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Koja je fora sa tim licemerjem?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.94,0:50:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pokupiš lutalicu sa ulice da bi se bolje osećao?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.68,0:50:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bilo ti je zanimljivo...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.18,0:50:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maltretirao si je zato što ne čuje, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.46,0:50:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A sada si našao da naučiš znakovni jezik?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.97,0:50:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Čemu sad to?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.80,0:50:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Misliš da si sad postao dobra osoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.66,0:50:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Odvratan si.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.89,0:50:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.59,0:50:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa da, čuo si od Nišimije.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.88,0:50:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, tako je.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.54,0:50:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam odvratno ljudsko biće.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.24,0:50:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Zapravo nemam prava da živim.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.92,0:50:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali poželeo sam da barem Nišimija više ne plače.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.04,0:51:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A, naravno, ne nameravam da se mešam među vas dvoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.01,0:51:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To se neće desiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.91,0:51:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali ovo sve moram i zbog sebe da uradim...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.10,0:51:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.05,0:51:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,U redu.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.46,0:51:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A, tako je.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.47,0:51:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini što ti sad rušim iluzije,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.38,0:51:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,ali ja sam Šokoina...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.16,0:51:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Znaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.98,0:51:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mlađa sestra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.80,0:51:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.96,0:52:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimijina majka...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.55,0:52:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Idemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.35,0:52:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, to boli.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.42,0:52:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.07,0:52:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Vratila sam se.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.39,0:52:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Juduru!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.43,0:52:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Seko?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.12,0:52:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Idvini! Idvini!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.36,0:52:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I meni je žao.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.85,0:52:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pije mi se bakin sok od perile.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.16,0:52:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Juzuru, bolje da se držiš podalje od onog dečaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.98,0:52:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci to i Šoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.67,0:52:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To ćemo same odlučiti,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.30,0:52:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,i ja i seka.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.00,0:52:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, momak.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.64,0:52:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ima?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.28,0:52:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si danas došao?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.88,0:52:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Da vratim pozajmljeni kišobran.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.93,0:52:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,O, momak.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.28,0:52:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Prilično si odgovoran.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.33,0:53:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka, to nije "momak".
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.82,0:53:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To je Nišimijina mlađa sestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.40,0:53:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, skapirao sam od ranije.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.18,0:53:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je što si prijateljica mom Jašou.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.85,0:53:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo je moj prijatelj Nagacuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.94,0:53:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nego,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.69,0:53:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,kupio sam mobilni.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.17,0:53:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, i ti ga imaš, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.13,0:53:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Da li razmenjuješ poruke sa prijateljima?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.10,0:53:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Iz srednje?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.33,0:53:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To je baš fino.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.68,0:53:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ima li još neko sa kime bi želela da razmenjuješ poruke?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.43,0:53:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Neko čiji bi broj želela da znaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.79,0:53:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A, pa da. Mogao bih da ti kažem moj...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.41,0:53:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.82,0:53:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa... ha... ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.22,0:54:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sahara, iz osnovne škole?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.38,0:54:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo, Jašo.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.58,0:54:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.68,0:54:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš li ići da nađeš tu Saharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.90,0:54:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A, pa hajde, nije tako.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.48,0:54:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali mislim da si ti baš odgovorna.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.04,0:54:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kavai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.75,0:54:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.70,0:54:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali, Mašiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.13,0:54:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kavai.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.45,0:54:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.73,0:54:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Želeo bih nešto da te pitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.17,0:54:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li možda imaš kontakt informacije od Sahare, iz osnovne škole?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.81,0:54:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sahare?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.60,0:54:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, nemam.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.56,0:54:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali znam u koju školu ide.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.27,0:54:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao ide u istu.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.44,0:54:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ženska akademija Taijo".
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.12,0:54:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do vraga. Švorc sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.85,0:54:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, uzmi ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.93,0:55:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta, bre? Ne treba mi toliko.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.84,0:55:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne brini o tome, Jašo.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.00,0:55:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Trebaće ti za put, hranu, i hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.29,0:55:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Biće ti lakše ako budeš imao bar ovoliko.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.54,0:55:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.20,0:55:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.76,0:55:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dovela sam je.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.20,0:55:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Seka se naljutila što je izostavljaš iako je ovo bila njena ideja.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.43,0:55:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, ali moraćeš da je povedeš, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.61,0:55:50.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,Jesi li umoran?\NJuzuru mi je dala tvoj broj.\NHvala ti na ovome.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.12,0:56:00.21,Signs,,0,0,0,,Bila sam jako srećna kada sam čula da si našao Saharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.21,0:56:05.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,Juzuru mi je ispričala puno o tebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.17,0:56:07.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti još jednom na ovome!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.27,0:56:19.64,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ženska akademija Taijo
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.46,0:56:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Da vidimo... Odavde idemo peške...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.87,0:56:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.52,0:56:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.28,0:56:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.77,0:56:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To sam ja, Sahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.76,0:56:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sećaš li me se?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.04,0:56:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.92,0:56:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha? Išida?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.08,0:56:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Davno se nismo videle, je l' tako?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.00,0:56:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Od onda sam nastavila da učim znakovni jezik.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.00,0:57:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li sam to dobro pokazala?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.75,0:57:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini što sam...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.84,0:57:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,iznenada nestala.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.69,0:57:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Od onda sam se uvek pitala šta je bilo sa tobom.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.22,0:57:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je što smo se ponovo videle.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.00,0:57:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Iznenadila sam se.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.76,0:57:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.08,0:57:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, da.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.19,0:57:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,U koju školu ti ideš?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.42,0:57:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.48,0:57:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nego, tvoje grudi su porasle.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.79,0:57:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji broj nosiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.11,0:57:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Daj da proverim!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.78,0:57:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.93,0:57:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Moram do toaleta.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.68,0:57:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha, u redu.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.14,0:57:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Delimo kupone za popust!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.24,0:57:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvolite.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.13,0:58:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Delimo kupone za popust!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.16,0:58:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.69,0:58:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Delimo kupone za popust!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.76,0:58:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvolite.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.04,0:58:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Posetite nas!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.10,0:58:23.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,Klub "Mjau mjau"
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.60,0:58:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Klub "Mjau mjau"?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.65,0:58:37.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sahara:\NSvaka čast, Išida, naučio si znakovni jezik?\NTakođe - hvala ti što si nas opet povezao!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.97,0:58:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Svaka čast Sahari.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.86,0:58:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ne bih mogao ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.49,0:58:43.87,Signs,,0,0,0,,Snimi video zapis
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.79,0:58:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Da nastavim ovako i povežem Nišimiju sa Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.11,0:58:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Nema šanse.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.96,0:58:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, i ja tako mislim.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.85,0:59:02.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,Klub "Mjau mjau"
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.51,0:59:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,U redu.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.74,0:59:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo li da uđemo, Nagacuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.63,0:59:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Napred, u klub "Mjau mjau"!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.35,0:59:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobrodo—
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.15,0:59:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobrodošli!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.88,0:59:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Koliko želite da ostanete?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.94,0:59:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Jedan sat, molim.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.62,0:59:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Imamo kupon za popust.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.72,0:59:16.56,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ozbiljno?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.56,0:59:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Naravno. Hvala vam.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.30,0:59:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne verujem, stvarno je došao.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.16,0:59:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Znaš, nekako...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.86,0:59:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta li si ti očekivao?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.40,0:59:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I ti isto?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.13,0:59:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne pričaj gluposti.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.47,0:59:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Došao sam vođen iskrenom željom da nađemo tvoju prijateljicu.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.09,0:59:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako je. Tvoju prijateljicu...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.64,0:59:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li ona ovde?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.29,0:59:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nismo baš prijatelji, doduše...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.24,0:59:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.51,0:59:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosta toga se desilo u šestom osnovne.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.36,0:59:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nismo se baš najprijatnije rastali.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.55,0:59:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne vidim je.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.08,1:00:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo li nazad, onda?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.16,1:00:06.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,Soba za testiranje sluha
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.32,1:00:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Buba!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.35,1:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A, došla si?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.45,1:00:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Došla sam da se igram sa Marijom.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.68,1:00:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Misliš li da bi se ovo svidelo Nišimiji?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.28,1:00:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maca!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.52,1:00:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulazim, seko!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.42,1:00:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Seko?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.71,1:00:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Poklon; staviću ga ovde.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.11,1:01:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,U...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.98,1:01:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.08,1:01:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go, go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.22,1:01:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.66,1:01:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Davno se nismo videli.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.73,1:01:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A, da.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.42,1:01:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Istina.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.06,1:01:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.98,1:01:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije to Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.36,1:01:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I dalje sama, vidim.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.92,1:01:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jadnica.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.87,1:01:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali stvarno, Išida, stvarno se nismo davno videli.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.43,1:01:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde neki put da se družimo.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.20,1:01:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Neka, hvala.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.12,1:01:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrziš me, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.73,1:01:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa ne baš.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.08,1:01:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uvek sam mislila kako sam trebala da ti pomognem nekako.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.69,1:01:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, za osnovnu.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.74,1:01:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A, Ueno. Siđi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.62,1:02:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije to torbica sa mog posla?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.12,1:02:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto je ima? Užas.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.04,1:02:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam joj je dao.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.64,1:02:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A, stvarno?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.55,1:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.82,1:02:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okej.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.71,1:02:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.07,1:02:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Davno se nismo videle, Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.47,1:02:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako si?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.59,1:02:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hej!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.15,1:02:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Nosiš samo jedan?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.40,1:02:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš, Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.76,1:02:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabavićemo se tako što ćemo ga baciti. Baš kao nekada.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.29,1:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.90,1:02:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Zezaš.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.06,1:02:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Zavitlavaš se, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.63,1:02:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stani malo.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.06,1:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Da vas dvoje možda ne izlazite?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.19,1:02:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Naravno da ne.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.28,1:03:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatelji smo.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.67,1:03:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatelji? Kakva šala!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.99,1:03:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatelj a maltretirao si je?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.08,1:03:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako to?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.11,1:03:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne vredi, ovo je presmešno.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.76,1:03:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zbog osećaja krivice?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.02,1:03:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.35,1:03:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, stvarno si postao jadan.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.87,1:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, želim vam da se zabavite igrajući se prijatelja.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.99,1:03:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta smo pričali?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.53,1:03:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ništa posebno.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.55,1:03:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Idem onda ja.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.44,1:03:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.95,1:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Juduru.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.94,1:04:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.50,1:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Juto je.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.70,1:04:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Budna sam. Od iznenađenja.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.44,1:04:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jedi douča—
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.79,1:04:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, ček... Pre toga...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.26,1:04:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.50,1:04:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Seko...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.57,1:04:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Danas imaš repić.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.60,1:04:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto...?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.96,1:04:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakvo čudno lice.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.00,1:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Moram da pokažem Išidi.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.97,1:04:39.27,Signs,,0,0,0,,Juzuru:\NGomila šarana danas.\NTreba neko da ih hrani. Dođi.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.03,1:04:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimi—
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.76,1:04:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Vezala je kosu u rep?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.94,1:05:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, ge ideš?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.99,1:05:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde idem?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.20,1:05:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do pekare.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.83,1:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Juzuru me je zamolila da kupim hleb za šarane.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.02,1:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Imamo dooljno. Juduru je šamo alaba.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.84,1:05:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.32,1:05:27.22,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ne molaš da kupi—
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.22,1:05:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj. Koristi znakovni jezik.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.40,1:05:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li dvučim šudno?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.24,1:05:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.63,1:05:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.50,1:05:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Skroz je u redu.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.11,1:05:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Moram da odem da kupim hleb.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.48,1:05:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.27,1:05:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.69,1:06:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Za mene?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.26,1:06:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.30,1:06:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogu li da pogledam?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.15,1:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je, bre, ovo?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.41,1:06:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.10,1:06:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...izađ.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.28,1:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.00,1:06:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ove?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.03,1:06:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...izađ.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.68,1:06:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Izađ sadmno!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.05,1:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Izašao... Mesec?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.22,1:07:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.39,1:07:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš je lep večeras.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.72,1:07:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.84,1:07:17.80,Signs,,0,0,0,,Slobodan? Hajmo na film!\NTvoj "veliki" prijatelj, Nagacuka.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.09,1:07:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci, Nagacuka.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.94,1:07:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li te ovo podseća na Mesec?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.85,1:07:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Na Mesec? Ne baš, ne.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.52,1:07:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Možd—
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.79,1:07:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Deluje da nisu slatkiši.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.40,1:07:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija mi je ih dala malopre.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.31,1:07:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno, šta li je ovo?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.55,1:07:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta se desilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.96,1:07:49.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,Pitala sam Išidu da izađe sa mnom.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.42,1:07:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zezaš?!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.84,1:07:55.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ali nije me skapirao.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.01,1:08:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A, promenila si frizuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.27,1:08:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si je promenila?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.62,1:08:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Da se nije nešto desilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.09,1:08:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš ti dobro stoji!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.84,1:08:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma hajde.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.26,1:08:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Samo sam žurila jutros.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.07,1:08:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno? Ali baš ti lepo stoji.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.69,1:08:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj, Kavai...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.86,1:08:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si promenila frizuru?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.04,1:08:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto, pitaš?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.62,1:08:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bez nekog posebnog razloga.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.54,1:08:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Takve su ti devojke.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.81,1:08:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.37,1:08:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.23,1:08:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pre neki dan je Mašiba rekao da bi želeo da bude tvoj prijatelj.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.53,1:08:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto si ti ovde?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.89,1:08:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je. Ja sam Sahara.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.20,1:08:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Zdravo. Ja sam Mašiba.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.92,1:08:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Stoj, bre!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.81,1:09:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde ćete mi preko glave?!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.44,1:09:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je da te vidim, Mijo!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.99,1:09:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, gde je Nišimija danas?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.06,1:09:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kući, rekla je da je boli stomak.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.08,1:09:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Da me ne izbegava?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.79,1:09:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.67,1:09:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pre neki dan je pokušavala nešto da mi saopšti, ali nisam mogao da je razumem.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.15,1:09:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je rekla?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.78,1:09:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Da je izašao... Mesec.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.51,1:09:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jednostavne reči, ali nisam razumeo njihov smisao.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.97,1:09:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, da, ne čudi me da se iznervirala.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.78,1:09:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, ako se brineš da te ne izbegava, zašto je ne pozoveš?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.24,1:09:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako ne bude htela da izađe, reći će tako.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.08,1:09:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako je...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.24,1:09:44.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hej... Nekoliko nas planira izlazak, hoćeš sa nama?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.34,1:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde prvo da stanemo u red ovamo!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.87,1:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Držite se blizu mene!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.95,1:10:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto je ona preuzela kontrolu?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.06,1:10:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemam pojma.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.40,1:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.43,1:10:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je sa njom?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.31,1:10:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponaša se previše prijateljski.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.15,1:10:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno? Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.71,1:10:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Neko poznat Šoko?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.47,1:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Da.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.14,1:10:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Iz osnovne.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.52,1:10:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Je l' slobodno tu, Sahara?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.41,1:10:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha. Izvoli.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.32,1:10:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pomalo je strašno.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.24,1:10:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeste li svi spremni?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.34,1:10:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesmo!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.16,1:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Krenimo onda!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.95,1:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Da ti možda ne smeta što je Ueno tu?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.87,1:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A, ne.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.04,1:10:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pohađamo isti smer u našoj školi.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.47,1:10:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Naučila sam puno od nje.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.83,1:11:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,U osnovnoj sam se plašila da se vozim rolerkosterom.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.19,1:11:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bila sam plašljivica.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.15,1:11:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali pokušala sam da promenim perspektivu.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.45,1:11:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rešila sam da neću odlučiti da li je strašno dok ne probam.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.05,1:11:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mada ipak jeste strašno.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.92,1:11:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eto ga.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.36,1:11:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, pazi, pazi!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.91,1:11:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Noge ti klecaju, Šo.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.32,1:11:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.70,1:11:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Strava.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.33,1:11:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Znaš znakovni jezik?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.00,1:12:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mora da si se baš trudio, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.87,1:12:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej! Šta je sa ovom rukom?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.96,1:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Vređaš mog Jašoa!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.04,1:12:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Samo sam druželjubiv.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.47,1:12:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Neće moći! Ne tako lako!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.39,1:12:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš si blesav, Nagacuka.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.00,1:12:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko želi da priđe Jašou mora da dobije moju dozvolu!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.98,1:12:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li tvoja kosa prirodna?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.40,1:12:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekini!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.08,1:12:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne diraj me!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.17,1:12:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.83,1:12:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Beži, Mašiba!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.12,1:12:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde, Jašo, stignimo ih!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.36,1:12:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.84,1:12:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Imam li ja prava da se ovoliko zabavljam?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.63,1:12:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ovo je nekako kao...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.12,1:12:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.66,1:12:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onako, kao da smo prijatelji!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.04,1:12:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.17,1:13:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Jede mi se takojaki.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.67,1:13:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde da ga kupimo.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.89,1:13:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Č-Ček.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.88,1:13:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Vaš takojaki.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.72,1:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.74,1:13:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušaj, Ueno.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.40,1:13:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo stvarno nije bilo potrebno.
Comment: 0,1:13:22.04,1:13:22.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,Umri, izdajice!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.87,1:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Š-Šimada?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.55,1:13:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Išida?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.95,1:13:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, javiću ti se!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.74,1:13:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.71,1:13:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li ljut?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.18,1:13:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.27,1:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam ljut.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.32,1:13:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Samo sam se nadala da biste mogli opet da se družite kao nekad.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.08,1:13:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislila sam da ćete naći zajednički jezik.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.24,1:13:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Niko ti to nije tražio.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.11,1:14:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.82,1:14:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam li i ja uradio istu stvar?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.13,1:14:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ti i ja smo slični.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.53,1:14:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nismo.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.01,1:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesmo.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.62,1:14:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nismo.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.85,1:14:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.00,1:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Svi bi bili srećni kada ne bi bilo Nišimije, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.20,1:14:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko si ti da to odlučiš?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.68,1:14:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali jednostavno je tako.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.90,1:14:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Da nje nije bilo, ne bi bilo problema između mene i Sahare.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.82,1:14:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A ti i Šimada biste ostali prijatelji.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.88,1:14:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Želim da sve bude kao nekad, pre nego što je ona došla.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.13,1:14:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Za to sa mnom i Šimadom...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.94,1:14:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam tako presekao i to je to.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.84,1:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, da li ti mene mrziš?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.90,1:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Verovatno.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.81,1:15:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislim da želim da se vozim na vrtešci.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.56,1:15:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ići ću sa Nišimijom.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.21,1:15:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.43,1:15:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija, vozi se sa mnom na vrtešci.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.57,1:15:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj, Ueno.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.99,1:15:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponesi ovo, seko.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.03,1:15:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ću još jedan krug na rolerkosteru.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.32,1:15:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A, zdravo, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.94,1:15:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Šoja je gore.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.10,1:15:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.05,1:15:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Imam strogo poverljivi snimak.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.20,1:15:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Snimak sa vrteške?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.16,1:15:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.32,1:15:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Kako?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.48,1:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ostavila sam da snima.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.96,1:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušaj.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.45,1:16:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja tebe mrzim.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.32,1:16:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ostavi to.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.92,1:16:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pričaću sporo tako da možeš da razumeš
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.74,1:16:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,i slušaću pažljivo kada ti govoriš.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.87,1:16:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,U osnovnoj školi,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.30,1:16:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,ja nisam imala razumevanja za tebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.14,1:16:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali ni ti nisi ni pokušala da razumeš mene, takođe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.40,1:16:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato si mi gurkala tvoju glupu svesku pod nos svaki čas
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.19,1:16:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,i uvek se blentavo smeškala.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.63,1:16:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A svaki put kada bi se nešto desilo, odmah si se izvinjavala.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.80,1:16:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato sam bila promenila svoj pristup.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.15,1:16:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorisala sam te, i ogovarala iza leđa.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.09,1:16:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To su bili znaci da mi se više ne približavaš.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.50,1:16:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali umesto da shvatiš te znake, ti si uzvratila.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.11,1:16:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Plačući si nas ocinkarila.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.92,1:17:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Zbog toga je Išida izgubio sve prijatelje.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.50,1:17:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sve oko nas se raspalo.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.49,1:17:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Idvini.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.14,1:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne želim da mi se izvinjavaš.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.74,1:17:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Obe smo radile šta smo morale,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.23,1:17:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,i sad kad pogledam, možda i nije moglo drugačije.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.70,1:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali nemam nameru da ti sada budem prijateljica.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.60,1:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I dalje te mrzim,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.28,1:17:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,i ti mrziš mene.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.96,1:17:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa zato šta kažeš da se ne forsiramo više?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.60,1:17:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rukujmo se kao dvoje ljudi koji se jednostavno mrze.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.32,1:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Grežiš.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.02,1:17:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja mržim šebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.13,1:17:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta, bre?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.32,1:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ti to znači?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.74,1:17:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I šta onda?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.87,1:17:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš li opet da mi se izviniš?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.61,1:18:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Na kraju je sve isto kao pre pet godina.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.86,1:18:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nećeš ni da pričaš sa mnom.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.58,1:18:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta misliš?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.21,1:18:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj... da...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.92,1:18:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Želim da Nišimija zavoli sebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.70,1:18:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno, beše?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.73,1:18:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, šta sa njom?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.12,1:18:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li se nešto desilo između nje i Nišimije?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.39,1:18:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha? Zašto pitaš?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.11,1:18:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kavai je rekla da se svašta izdešavalo u osnovnoj školi.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.25,1:18:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija stvarno ne čuje, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.62,1:18:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.55,1:18:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj, da nije zato maltretirana?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.66,1:19:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ne podnosim takve stvari.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.00,1:19:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar se ne slažeš, Išida?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.58,1:19:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha? Kako to misliš?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.65,1:19:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš da kažeš da ja tu širim neke priče o prošlosti?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.68,1:19:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Č-Ček, glasna si.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.83,1:19:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uopšte se nisi promenio.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.51,1:19:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ostao si užasan kao i u osnovnoj.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.63,1:19:21.05,Alt,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo, Jašo?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.05,1:19:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiri se, Kavai.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.98,1:19:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,O čemu ste pričali?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.42,1:19:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mašiba, Išida je nekada maltretirao jednu devojčicu.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.24,1:19:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to pričaš, Kavai?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.87,1:19:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nema šanse...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.25,1:19:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Istina je!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.29,1:19:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I ti si je ogovarala.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.85,1:19:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja nikada nisam ogovarala Nišimiju.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.60,1:19:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimiju?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.67,1:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako je! Išida je maltretirao Nišimiju!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.70,1:19:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Znaš, ja sam pokušala da ga zaustavim.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.06,1:19:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali on nije slušao.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.23,1:20:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bilo je strašno.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.14,1:20:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.92,1:20:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li do—
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.30,1:20:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, Nagacuka.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.29,1:20:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.34,1:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.26,1:20:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ja mrzim sebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.40,1:20:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.44,1:20:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.22,1:21:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.71,1:21:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Ništa.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.73,1:21:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.61,1:21:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tu si, Išida!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.72,1:21:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Doneo sam tvoju torbu.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.90,1:21:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Poz.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.72,1:21:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.08,1:21:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam je pozvala.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.56,1:21:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini za ono ranije.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.16,1:21:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali ionako je sve bila tvoja krivica.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.72,1:21:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ipak, Mašiba je rekao da bi trebalo da ti oprostim, ako se izviniš Nišimiji.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.12,1:21:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj malo.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.06,1:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To je glupost.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.19,1:21:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi nemamo prava da kritikujemo Išidu u vezi sa time.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.21,1:21:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mi"?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.80,1:21:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisi u pravu, Nao.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.47,1:21:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako to nisam?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.20,1:21:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Za razliku od mene, ti si se trudila da je maltretiraš.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.28,1:21:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne trpaj me u isti koš.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.65,1:22:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.68,1:22:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.45,1:22:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.46,1:22:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uopšte nismo iste. Ti si se samo smejala i oponašala me!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.93,1:22:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Užasna si!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.09,1:22:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ti kažeš, Sahara?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.58,1:22:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.80,1:22:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nao je i tebe stalno ogovarala, Sahara!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.23,1:22:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Govorila sam samo istinu!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.60,1:22:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci, Sahara, kako je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.80,1:22:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Ja...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.40,1:22:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam se plašila vas obe nekada.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.38,1:22:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Na čijoj si ti strani?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.72,1:22:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ničijoj!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.44,1:22:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosta više.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.29,1:22:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sve je moja krivica.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.01,1:22:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrzim takvo razmišljanje.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.94,1:22:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.02,1:22:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj sve da odlučuješ u tuđe ime.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.20,1:22:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, ne moraš baš tako...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.86,1:22:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosta više, Sahara.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.43,1:23:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ionako ćeš samo opet da pobegneš i zažališ što si bila plašljiva.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.46,1:23:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je sa tobom, Išida?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.45,1:23:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosta više, Kavai.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.26,1:23:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oduvek si samo brinula za sebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.24,1:23:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.40,1:23:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam tvoj saveznik.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.17,1:23:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pusti me više, ni ne poznaješ me kako treba, kakav saveznik?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.59,1:23:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosta više, ja odlazim!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.17,1:23:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.96,1:23:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,U redu je.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.37,1:23:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Meni ne smeta.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.06,1:23:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.44,1:23:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.93,1:23:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.84,1:23:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije trebalo da dođem.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.37,1:23:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida, užasan si.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.64,1:23:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemaš veze sa ovime, ne mešaj se.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.70,1:23:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A mislio sam da smo postali prijatelji.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.38,1:24:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A, da.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.46,1:24:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sledeće nedelje počinje letnji raspust.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.84,1:24:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš da idemo negde...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.63,1:24:38.51,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nemam pojma.\NIzvini.\NSlušaš li me?!\NIzvini.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.04,1:24:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Juzu?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.33,1:24:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Vid će ti se iskvariti ako budeš čitala u mraku.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.42,1:24:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Evo.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.31,1:25:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Još uvek se brineš za svoju sestru?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.56,1:25:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Baka se brine za tebe, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.87,1:25:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stalno razmišljaš o sestri.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.69,1:25:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A sebe ostavljaš po strani.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.04,1:25:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa i ti si ista, bako.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.38,1:25:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne ideš u klub penzionera, već učiš znakovni jezik.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.87,1:25:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja to radim za sebe, pa je u redu.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.93,1:25:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Onda i ja to radim za sebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.84,1:25:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li tako?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.46,1:25:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ti si dobra devojčica.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.05,1:25:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Misliš?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.39,1:25:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama stalno viče na mene.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.25,1:25:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam ni u školu išla odavno.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.75,1:25:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Srce ti je čisto.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.93,1:25:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I Šoko se trudi.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.11,1:25:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Blagoslovena sam divnim unukama.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.64,1:26:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uzmi i zemičke.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.53,1:26:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoću.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.56,1:26:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bako...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.20,1:26:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Nišimija. Kako si?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.65,1:26:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Danas imam neki baš fini hleb.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.85,1:26:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj hleb...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.48,1:26:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobar je, nalik tebi.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.71,1:26:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I zato...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.31,1:26:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to pričam, pobogu?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.84,1:26:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.47,1:26:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar neće da dođe danas?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.46,1:26:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.04,1:27:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Da te opet ne boli stomak?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.25,1:27:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne, to je čudno.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.15,1:27:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Juzu—
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.25,1:27:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ili da idem kući.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.14,1:27:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.40,1:27:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.46,1:27:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako si to obučena?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.01,1:27:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa u uniformu, prirodno.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.26,1:27:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako izgledam?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.83,1:27:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.86,1:27:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa za školu.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.54,1:27:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije sada letnji raspust?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.19,1:27:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci stvarno, šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.18,1:27:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ništa.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.87,1:27:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Recimo da sam se spremila za maskenbal.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.54,1:28:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seka. Moram da idem.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.25,1:28:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Otpratiću te. Gde ideš?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.77,1:28:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne moraš.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.35,1:28:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma hajde.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.28,1:28:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno nema potrebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.60,1:28:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Plakala si malopre, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.21,1:28:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.56,1:28:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nema nikakve veze sa tobom.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.43,1:28:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ima, ili bar tako želim da mislim.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.00,1:28:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.68,1:28:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato što se brinem za tebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.38,1:28:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj sad i ti da pričaš kao moja baka.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.47,1:28:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro onda, kako god.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.99,1:28:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.02,1:28:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ovde je dovoljno.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.96,1:28:45.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sahrana - Nišimija Ito
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.65,1:28:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.59,1:28:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Drži se, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.86,1:28:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.99,1:29:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ipak je strašno.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.16,1:30:05.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hej, Nišimija. Hoćemo negde sutra?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.15,1:31:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Strava!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.66,1:31:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde da bacimo pogled.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.23,1:31:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.95,1:31:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oladih se.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.16,1:31:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto se izvinjavaš?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.08,1:31:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Naravno da ne!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.92,1:31:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta kažeš da smislimo i nešto za sutra?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.37,1:31:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Može, Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.92,1:31:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rekla je da ću biti nesrećan ako budem provodio vreme sa njom.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.64,1:31:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meni, onome ko je izazvao svu njenu nesreću.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.43,1:32:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Želim da vidim more.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.88,1:32:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Želim da volim ljude.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.38,1:32:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Čak i čudovišta imaju srca...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.48,1:32:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne znam kako ću ikada sve ispraviti.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.39,1:32:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.41,1:32:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej, danas je i Juzuru sa nama? Super!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.25,1:32:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo da gledamo film?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.88,1:32:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš zabavno!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.87,1:32:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.80,1:32:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dođoh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.40,1:32:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Čoveče, ovo je najbolji raspust ikad!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.73,1:32:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ne, Juzuru?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.83,1:32:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ja znam...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.73,1:32:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali stvarno, svaki dan je bio vrh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.40,1:32:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.64,1:32:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde ćemo sutra?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.38,1:32:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajdemo i sutra negde.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.01,1:33:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne možemo sutra. Imamo planove.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.34,1:33:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.64,1:33:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li luda, seko?!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.40,1:33:07.64,Alt,,0,0,0,,Šta pravite?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.04,1:33:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li ovo u redu?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.64,1:33:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Smem li ja da budem ovde?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.85,1:33:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Imaš misiju da nam pomogneš da napravimo tortu za rođendan naše majke.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.57,1:33:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoće li to biti u redu?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.34,1:33:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Da ne dobijem opet šamar?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.11,1:33:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pusti šamar, možda te i ubije.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.84,1:33:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.32,1:33:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Izgleda odlično!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.42,1:33:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radite?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.79,1:33:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto je on ovde, Šoko?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.82,1:33:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta pokušavaš?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.04,1:33:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Napolje.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.04,1:33:37.38,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hajde, hajde, mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.38,1:33:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta fali? Danas proslavljamo.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.09,1:33:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.41,1:33:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro ti stoji.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.92,1:33:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Njam!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.64,1:33:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Izgleda da si nekako ostao živ, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.58,1:33:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Da.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.88,1:33:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uspele smo, seko.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.78,1:33:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nego, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.86,1:34:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Poslala sam jednu tvoju fotografiju na regionalno takmičenje.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.42,1:34:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ček, šta?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.01,1:34:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo je htela da probamo.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.68,1:34:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta? Ali to su sve neke uvrnute slike.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.66,1:34:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije baš tako.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.38,1:34:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Što mi tu spletkarite iza leđa?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.88,1:34:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nego.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.10,1:34:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sledećeg utorka će biti veliki vatromet, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.28,1:34:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A, neka, preskočiću.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.91,1:34:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma hajde.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.32,1:34:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Da li je ovde u redu?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.53,1:34:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.47,1:35:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A, idem da kupim jakisobu.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.31,1:35:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde sa mnom.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.60,1:35:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.31,1:35:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A, i hvala što ste me pozvale kući pre neki dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.39,1:35:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li vaša majka...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.57,1:35:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha. Da li je bila srećna?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.69,1:35:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam mogao da procenim po izrazu.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.24,1:35:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kada je tvoj rođendan?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.53,1:35:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedmi jun?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.90,1:35:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa već je prošao, znači!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.28,1:35:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Znači već imaš osamnaest, je li?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.46,1:36:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde da proslavimo tvoj sledeći rođendan zajedno, okej?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.48,1:36:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ajoj, rekao sam "zajedno"!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.46,1:36:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A, tako znači?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.54,1:36:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.40,1:36:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.48,1:36:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali vatromet još nije završen.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.21,1:36:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Moraš da učiš?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.62,1:36:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A, u redu.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.21,1:36:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Otpratiću te.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.92,1:36:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.38,1:37:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako dakle.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.51,1:37:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se onda.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.41,1:37:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.92,1:37:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gde je seka?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.19,1:37:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nego, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.81,1:37:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Možeš li da mi doneseš foto-aparat?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.30,1:37:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinjavam se...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.08,1:37:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji mrak.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.47,1:37:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.17,1:37:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ulazim.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.79,1:37:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eto ga.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.42,1:37:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li napunjen?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.57,1:37:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I odavde se vidi vatromet?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.63,1:37:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A, eto je.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.81,1:37:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.60,1:38:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.28,1:38:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Č-Č-Čekaj malo.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.67,1:38:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš, Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.86,1:38:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.79,1:38:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.59,1:38:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.12,1:38:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Šoko!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.52,1:39:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.04,1:39:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto, Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.63,1:39:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija, zgrabi ivicu!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.96,1:39:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bože.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.05,1:39:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Molim te daj mi još samo malo snage.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.07,1:39:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Neću više bežati od stvari.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.70,1:39:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Od sutra,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.48,1:39:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}gledaću ljude u lice.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.48,1:39:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Od sutra, slušaću njihove glasove.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.43,1:39:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Od sutra, ispraviću stvari.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.39,1:39:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.29,1:39:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ja sam joj bio zadao taj ožiljak.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.54,1:39:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jesam li joj se izvinio kako treba?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.07,1:39:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.52,1:39:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Izvini, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.88,1:39:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Da li se još uvek ljutiš?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.82,1:39:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čoveče, baš sam zeznuo.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.82,1:40:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trebao sam da te pitam šta misliš o meni.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.66,1:40:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nego, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.19,1:40:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vidiš, ja...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.86,1:40:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Šo.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.12,1:40:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoja sestra je ispekla palačinke.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.58,1:40:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Marija će da vidi vatromet!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.18,1:40:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hladno...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.48,1:40:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ali toplo...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.85,1:40:53.56,Signs,,0,0,0,,Lokalna bolnica Sumion
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.05,1:41:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Teto!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.71,1:41:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A, Juzuru!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.39,1:41:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Konačno sam te našla.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.02,1:41:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,U radnji se niko nije javljao.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.35,1:41:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A ovde su rekli da su posete zabranjene.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.62,1:41:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sada je u redu.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.61,1:41:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Od danas su ga premestili.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.94,1:41:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde sa mnom, da ga vidiš.{?}{zapravo obrnuto, da ti vidi lice, ali on je u komi, tako da...?}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.41,1:41:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Teto, Šoko je...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.23,1:41:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gospođo Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.19,1:41:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gospođo Nišimija?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.93,1:41:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinite, jako mi je žao.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.82,1:41:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Opet smo vam izazvali probleme.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.14,1:41:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Istinski se izvinjavam.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.69,1:41:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemojte, molim vas!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.28,1:41:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sigurna sam da je moj sin ponovo uradio nešto vašoj Šoko.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.44,1:41:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,U suprotnom...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.20,1:41:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Teto, on je spasao moju glupu sestru.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.05,1:41:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam bila isuviše nepažljiva.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.04,1:41:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.48,1:42:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim vas...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.64,1:42:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim vas, ustanite.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.00,1:42:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Meni je samo drago da je Šoko u redu.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.99,1:42:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I ti, Juzuru.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.28,1:42:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim vas.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.17,1:42:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto je Išida morao da se povredi?!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.34,1:42:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekini da izigravaš neku tragičnu heroinu!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.03,1:42:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Reci nešto.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.91,1:42:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Toliko sam namučila ljude oko sebe, i to mi je jako teško palo,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.41,1:42:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,pa sam pokušala da se ubijem.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.72,1:42:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinjavam se.", je l' da?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.08,1:42:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Koliko si samo uobražena?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.41,1:42:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ti si prokleta pošast, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.01,1:42:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Najviše mrzim takve kao što si ti,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.22,1:42:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,one koji ne mogu da sagledaju situaciju iz tuđe perspektive!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.97,1:42:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.18,1:42:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko si, bre, ti?!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.35,1:42:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li ti njena majka?!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.39,1:42:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekinite...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.99,1:43:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta rađaš decu ako ne možeš da se staraš o njima!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.56,1:43:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radite?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.25,1:43:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.13,1:43:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekinite!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.83,1:43:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.62,1:43:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radite?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.09,1:43:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li ti Šoko?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.08,1:43:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ižvin...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.56,1:43:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ižvinite...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.16,1:43:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ižvinite!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.25,1:43:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ižvinite!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.49,1:43:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ižvinite!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.42,1:44:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to radiš?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.92,1:44:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nekada sam mislila da seka neće hteti da se ubije ako vidi ove slike.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.50,1:44:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je trebalo da učinim?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.39,1:45:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Neće da se otvore.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.60,1:45:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Drži ih zatvorenim!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.30,1:45:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A, nisam te video, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.81,1:45:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo negde da sednemo? Ja častim.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.28,1:45:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Čuo sam šta se desilo sa Jašom.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.21,1:45:26.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,Uništila sam sve što je Išida izgradio.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.51,1:45:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Misliš na ono što se desilo na mostu?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.08,1:45:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo je prihvatio čudaka kao što sam ja.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.61,1:45:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Učinio je da po prvi put shvatim šta je to najbolji prijatelj.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.76,1:45:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo je moj "veliki" prijatelj, i stvarno želim da se probudi.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.03,1:46:00.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Želim da popravim ono što sam uništila.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.61,1:46:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar da ti padne na pamet da se ubiješ zato što ti je teško!?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.78,1:46:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kavai, preglasna si.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.19,1:46:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ona me neće čuti ako ne budem glasna.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.30,1:46:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako smo se brinuli!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.01,1:46:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Svi prolaze kroz neke poteškoće tokom života.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.89,1:46:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To važi za sve nas, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.18,1:46:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato moraš da naučiš da voliš i svoje loše osobine kako bi nastavila da koračaš napred.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.69,1:46:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je da si dobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.95,1:46:43.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,Želim da popravim ono što sam uništila.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.93,1:46:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Razumem.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.21,1:46:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pričala si sa svima?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.85,1:46:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaka si.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.33,1:46:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja nemam toliko samopouzdanja.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.73,1:47:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne znam kako ću da se suočim sa Išidom kada se probudi.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.65,1:47:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja nisam uspela da se promenim.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.92,1:47:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Opet nisam uspela da te zaštitim!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.41,1:47:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I dalje sam plašljivica.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.70,1:47:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pomeničeš še od šada,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.98,1:47:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahada...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.70,1:47:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti što si došla, Šo.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.83,1:48:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bre, prekini više.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.42,1:48:16.97,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.67,1:48:19.84,Signs,,0,0,0,,Našao sam te.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.39,1:48:23.85,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kako si?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.56,1:48:25.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,Znaš,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.18,1:48:28.85,Signs,,0,0,0,,ovo je nekako čudno, ha?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.31,1:48:30.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ja...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.56,1:48:32.73,Signs,,0,0,0,,želeo sam da umrem...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.40,1:48:34.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,A.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.94,1:48:37.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,Još malo pa je prošao utorak.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.32,1:48:39.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.07,1:48:41.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.19,1:49:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.44,1:49:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je ovo?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.39,1:49:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.44,1:49:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Skidajte ovo sa mene!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.24,1:50:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.86,1:50:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.01,1:50:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.80,1:50:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.79,1:50:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.90,1:50:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.97,1:51:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.51,1:51:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je da si dobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.34,1:51:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.73,1:51:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam sada dobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.79,1:51:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Manje - više.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.40,1:51:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj tako da me gledaš, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.32,1:51:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A, da.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.80,1:51:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.14,1:52:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.25,1:52:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam se stvarno izvinio za sve ono što sam ti učinio u prošlosti.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.97,1:52:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A ni za ono kasnije.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.76,1:52:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Verovatno sam u svojoj glavi stvorio sliku tebe kakva mi je odgovarala.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.17,1:52:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Želeo sam više da pričam sa tobom.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.00,1:52:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Verovatno je to bilo sve.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.11,1:52:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali ja sam te povredio
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.58,1:52:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,i naterao da napraviš najgori mogući izbor.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.93,1:52:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.31,1:52:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ti ši pao žato što ja nišam mogla da se pomenim!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.42,1:52:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Šve je moja kvivica!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.90,1:52:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Da šamo mene nie bilo...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.30,1:53:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ižvini!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.24,1:53:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim te, ne plači, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.33,1:53:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušaj, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.05,1:53:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pričao sam sa tobom do malopre.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.38,1:53:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bilo je to u snu.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.33,1:53:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Izgledalo je da sam odustao od svega.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.08,1:53:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali to nije bilo ispravno.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.17,1:53:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I ja sam ranije razmišljao slično kao ti,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.64,1:53:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,ali sam ipak shvatio da ne zaslužujem da umrem.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.86,1:53:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Želim da se izvinim i ostalima.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.88,1:53:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušaj, Nišimija. Ja...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.25,1:54:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja želim da mi pomogneš da živim.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.98,1:54:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.80,1:54:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Ha?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.13,1:54:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesam li ja upravo rekao nešto mnogo čudno?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.14,1:54:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ajoj!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.63,1:54:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Izvini! Zaboravi to!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.88,1:54:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboravi to što sam sad rekao!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.06,1:55:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stigli smo na vaše odredište, {\i1}gospodine{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.83,1:55:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej, Marija. Zalivaš cveće?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.14,1:55:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Baš si dobra devojčica.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.72,1:55:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš li da umreš?!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.84,1:55:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Marija, Šo je oživeo.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.34,1:55:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam umro, Marija.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.36,1:55:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nije li to Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.26,1:55:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ona se starala o tebi sve vreme.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.04,1:55:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Idi zahvali joj se.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.35,1:55:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Čujem da si dolazila da me posetiš.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.78,1:55:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam užasna osoba.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.65,1:55:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Čak ni u ovakvoj situaciji, nisam mogla da se zbližim sa Nišimijom.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.20,1:55:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mada možda i nije bilo potrebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.64,1:56:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A, nego, oni koji su te izvukli iz vode kada si pao su bili Šimada i Hirose.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.85,1:56:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mada rekli su mi da ti ne kažem.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.05,1:56:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.13,1:56:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobrodošao nazad.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.93,1:56:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, odoh sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.31,1:56:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.89,1:56:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pobogu. Pa ovo je previše kratko!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.31,1:56:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo vam stoji mnogo bolje.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.03,1:56:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A, dobrodošao nazad, Šo.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.70,1:56:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinjavam se na smetnji.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.71,1:56:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dobar dan.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.73,1:56:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.72,1:56:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.29,1:56:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.68,1:56:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A, ne...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.97,1:56:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I ja se izvinjavam.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.15,1:56:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako je. Moj sin je neuništiv.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.46,1:56:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Majka!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.40,1:56:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Idem da pokupim Mariju.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.19,1:56:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okej.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.27,1:56:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko je to?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.86,1:56:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Moj zet. Vratio se.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.96,1:56:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A, Šo.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.39,1:56:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Juzuru je gore.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.30,1:57:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Daj joj žele iz frižidera.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.34,1:57:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,'Ej.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.61,1:57:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Zimska uniforma?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.69,1:57:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro ti stoji.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.75,1:57:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidi ovo, Išida.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.25,1:57:10.21,Signs,,0,0,0,,Fotografsko takmičenje - dobitnik učeničke nagrade\NNišimija Juzuru (3. razred niže srednje)
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.99,1:57:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Zezaš! Strava!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.39,1:57:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A vidi i ovo.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.59,1:57:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Zezaš? Strašno...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.57,1:57:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim te, šefe!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.99,1:57:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Podučavaj me!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.34,1:57:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A, pa dobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.39,1:57:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Počela si da ideš u školu, znači?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.07,1:57:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Šoko me je motivisala.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.53,1:57:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, daću sve od sebe.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.70,1:57:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Da ne izneverim nikoga.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.93,1:57:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Čujem sutra imaš školski festival?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.28,1:57:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Da, tako je.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.49,1:57:49.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,Nišimija: Dolazimo na festival sutra.\NČekaću pred kapijom u 10.\NJuzuru i mama će doći kasnije.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.04,1:57:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dobro jutro, narode.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.16,1:57:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako ste?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.83,1:57:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinite za užasne stvari što sam rekao.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.20,1:58:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okej!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.44,1:58:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Odoh.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.44,1:58:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Čuvaj se.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.83,1:58:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Je l' se to tako koristi?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.52,1:58:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta to?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.43,1:58:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A, nema veze.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.57,1:58:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Vidimo se.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.01,1:58:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Srećno!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.96,1:58:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro jutro.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.30,1:58:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo li?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:51.02,1:58:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije to Išida?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.98,1:58:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.21,1:58:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Onaj hospitalizovan?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.53,1:58:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Što je skočio?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.47,1:59:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam ti ovo rekao ranije,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.83,1:59:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,ali ja se ne uklapam najbolje u svoju školu.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.64,1:59:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne mogu da gledam ljude u lice.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.16,1:59:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato mi je lakše kada gledam dole, u pod.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.55,1:59:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogu da gledam dole?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.01,1:59:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:28.91,1:59:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogu da hodam i sam...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.19,1:59:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti, Nišimija.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.12,1:59:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo je moje odeljenje.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.63,1:59:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Je li voda spremna?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.21,1:59:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Još samo malo.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.40,1:59:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:42.44,1:59:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To je Išida!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.36,1:59:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li ozdravio?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.14,1:59:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nišimija...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.51,1:59:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mislim da me je stomak malo zaboleo.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.32,1:59:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.49,1:59:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.60,2:00:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:12.22,2:00:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.98,2:00:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo, boli te stomak?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:18.93,2:00:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.34,2:00:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Nagacuka. Dobro jutro.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.66,2:00:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako si?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.08,2:00:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Što se tiče onoga—
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.63,2:00:27.77,Alt,,0,0,0,,Zašto gledaš na dole?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.77,2:00:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Baš čudno.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.52,2:00:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Zapravo sam hteo da te pogledam pravo u oči.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:34.13,2:00:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Da se nisam uplašio?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.81,2:00:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Jašo.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.12,2:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.16,2:00:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tako mi je drago što si dobro.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.88,2:00:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Da se nisi...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:46.14,2:00:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Da se nisi probudio, sa mnom bi bilo gotovo!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.17,2:00:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:53.13,2:00:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da brineš za ono što se desilo na mostu.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.59,2:00:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Takve stvari se dešavaju u životu.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.09,2:01:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Zato, molim te, Jašo...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.90,2:01:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne idi nigde!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.36,2:01:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Molim te!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.14,2:01:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:10.24,2:01:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini, za sve.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:15.28,2:01:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.64,2:01:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jašo.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.75,2:01:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A, i takođe...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.06,2:01:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je sa tim brkovima?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:23.22,2:01:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To je bio deo molitve, da se probudiš što pre.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.90,2:01:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagacuka...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:35.81,2:01:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.88,2:01:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Čuo sam Nagacuku kako uzvikuje tvoje ime.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.68,2:01:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:43.24,2:01:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kavai, trebalo bi da ih daš Išidi.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.68,2:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Donela si ih?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.48,2:01:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Donela sam ih, ali ne mogu da mu ih dam. Nisu ispali dobro.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:52.21,2:01:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa šta fali? Hajde da mu damo.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.04,2:02:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Evo.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.21,2:02:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Zapravo sam želela da skupim hiljadu komada, ali nisam uspela.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.21,2:02:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Zamolila sam sve, ali...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.44,2:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:11.86,2:02:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Ne, ovo je neverovatno!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.60,2:02:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo je sasvim dovoljno!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.87,2:02:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikada nisam dobio ovako nešto,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:17.20,2:02:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,pa sam baš, stvarno, srećan.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.62,2:02:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti, Kavai.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.24,2:02:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I izvini.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.30,2:02:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I ti, Mašiba.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.93,2:02:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne, tebi svaka čast.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.38,2:02:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Odvratno.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.57,2:02:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Igrate se prijatelja?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:31.30,2:02:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Koža mi se naježila.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.69,2:02:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto moraš da budeš takva?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:35.60,2:02:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.35,2:02:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je sa tobom, Kavai? Hoćeš svađu sa mnom?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.83,2:02:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, hej, smirite se.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.00,2:02:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Išida...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:43.69,2:02:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.87,2:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Toliko si se mučio, a nisam mogla da ti pomognem.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.56,2:02:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uopšte se nisam promenila.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.59,2:02:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj tako.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:54.49,2:02:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I ja sam isti.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.12,2:03:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne pričaju ni o čemu ozbiljnom.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:02.70,2:03:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Opet si se izvinila.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:05.48,2:03:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, takva si i šta je tu je.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.01,2:03:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Glupačo.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:15.28,2:03:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Glupačo.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.59,2:03:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Glupačo.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.30,2:03:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A, bre, zaboravi.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.11,2:03:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Idem da pojedem nešto.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:28.75,2:03:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pobegla je.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:29.83,2:03:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Postidela se.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.25,2:03:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Slušajte, želeo bih nešto da vas zamolim.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.16,2:03:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Smem li?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:40.69,2:03:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Želeo bih da svi zajedno prošetamo festivalom.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.18,2:04:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Čoveče, ovo je baš ukusno!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:06.12,2:04:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde posle da pogledamo u salu.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:08.46,2:04:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobro je smeo da dođe u školu.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.78,2:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, tezga odeljenja B je strava.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.44,2:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Idemo.
